Slight correction per additional evidence: the white sample ballots in Person Cty appear to be marked “Local candidates in good standing are circled. (In accordance with 2022 Plan of Organization, Person County GOP.)” If you see something, say something NC!
If anyone sees other instances, please share or reach out to me. Again, this is flagrant election manipulation before a Primary. #ncpol #ncsen

The GOP in Person Cty was reportedly told by Board of Elections officials that they could not distribute the sample ballot b/c it was on white paper- same color as actual ballot. GOP reportedly continued to distribute these sample ballots after being told to stop….#ncpol #ncsen

I now have evidence that Person County GOP was also handing out pre-marked sample ballots with preferred candidates. The ballots were not marked with any funding or sponsoring org and were printed on white paper as in Moore County…
#ncpol #ncsen

@cherylinperil The sample ballot from the State Board of Elections was printed out. Bubbles were filled in next to “recommended” candidates in each section and photocopied. The ballot had no additional markings about funding org, etc., and was being passed out from a GOP tent outside two polls.
For clarification, these are sample ballots.

Moore Cty GOP is endorsing specific Primary candidates & handing out completed & unattributable ballots at polling places. Primary candidates are handing out literature under GOP tents. I heard this for Aberdeen and Carthage. This is flagrant election manipulation. #ncpol #ncsen
